article_node.title: The Pixel 10 Pro XL Goes to Paris: Out of Hundreds of Photos, These Are My Favs
article_node.summary: The Google Pixel 10 Pro and 10 Pro XL, featuring a Tensor G5 processor and enhanced AI tools, maintain a similar camera setup to their predecessors, with a 50MP main camera and 5x optical zoom. While the design remains largely unchanged, the new models promise improved performance and battery life, alongside innovative AI features like ProRes Zoom and Camera Coach. Set to launch on August 28, the phones will offer various storage options and are expected to retain the pricing structure of the Pixel 9 line.
